      다양한 사람들과 소통하며 생각을 듣고 공유하는걸 좋아합니다.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a
        href="https://github.com/dding-g"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-blue-500 underline">Github</a
      >

      <a
        href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/ddingg/"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-blue-500 underline">Linkedin</a
      >

      <a
        href="https://dding-g.notion.site/1929dabeb9c7809eb426fc293e142128?v=1929dabeb9c7808399e1000cc5282642&pvs=4"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-blue-500 underline">가벼운 기록</a
